```plantuml
@startuml inovex_scrumlr.io

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend API" as BE
participant "WebSocket Service" as WS
participant "Database" as DB

User -> FE: Open Scrumlr.io
FE -> BE: Authenticate User
BE -> DB: Query User Data
DB --> BE: Return User Data
BE --> FE: Return Auth Token

User -> FE: Create New Board
FE -> BE: POST /api/boards
BE -> DB: Insert New Board
DB --> BE: Confirm Insert
BE -> WS: Notify Board Created
WS -> FE: Update Client with New Board
BE --> FE: Return Board Data

User -> FE: Add Note to Board
FE -> BE: POST /api/boards/{boardId}/notes
BE -> DB: Insert Note
DB --> BE: Confirm Insert
BE -> WS: Notify Note Added
WS -> FE: Update Client with New Note
BE --> FE: Return Note Data

User -> FE: Vote on Note
FE -> BE: POST /api/boards/{boardId}/notes/{noteId}/vote
BE -> DB: Update Vote Count
DB --> BE: Confirm Update
BE -> WS: Notify Vote Updated
WS -> FE: Update Client with New Vote Count
BE --> FE: Return Updated Vote Count

User -> FE: Export Board Data
FE -> BE: GET /api/boards/{boardId}/export
BE -> DB: Retrieve Board Data
DB --> BE: Return Board Data
BE --> FE: Return Exported Data

@enduml
```